vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Specific Use Permit for a community service center use on property zoned an MF-2(A) Multifamily District, on the south line of Laughlin Drive, west line of Avenue Q
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval for a three-year period, subject to a site plan and conditions
Z201-177(CT)
